<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,326,1615,1639]" pageId="44" pageNumber="45">Etymology</emphasis>
.
</emphasis>
The species name is a Greek name of a person. We consider it to be a latinized noun used in apposition.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
